<HEADLINE>
ATTN EDITORS:  

</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   JACOBY-COLUMN-BOS (k) by Jeff Jacoby, will be unavailable until
Thursday, July 9.
</P>
<P>
   After that date, Jacoby columns will move Monday and Thursday,
instead of the previous Tuesday and Thursday.
