SPECIAL WOMEN'S HEALTH STORIES We are offering a selection of
features - plus art - from a special New York Times 'Women's
Health' section which covers a range of health issues and addresses
every stage of a woman's life. (In most households, the woman is
the healthcare gatekeeper.) The stories will help your readers
understand the medical innovations and trends that affect women --
and the lives of those around them:
</P>
