</P>
<P>
   NIRELAND-VOTE (Belfast) _ The Northern Ireland peace process
marks another milestone in its bullets-to-ballots passage as
residents of the contentious province turn out in large numbers to
elect members of a new legislature. By Warren Hoge.
</P>
<P>
   LEBANON-PRISONERS (Jerusalem) _ Israel confirmed on Thursday
that it was ready to release 60 Lebanese prisoners and return to
Lebanon the remains of 40 slain anti-Israel fighters in return for
the remains of an Israeli soldier. By Joel Greenberg.
</P>
