   LOUISIANA-CASINOS-TEX (Kinder, La.) _ For thousands of gamblers
from cities around Texas, a bus ride to the casino is the low and
short road to the Vegas-style action. And it's virtually a vacation
jackpot. The casinos subsidize the bus trips for players and often
throw in a free meal and complimentary drinks. By John MacCormack.
</P>
