   MEXICO-CRUISE-BOS (Aboard the Elation) _ From swimming pools to
the on-board Slots Tournament, the Carnival ship Elation is drawing
twentysomethings and older crowds who want to see the Mexican
Riviera at a leisurely pace. The cruise line also is targeting
families _ the Elation includes a playground and day care center.
By Julie Cooper.
</P>
