<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-25 17:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7025 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SIGHT-FILM-REVIEW-NYT     06-25 1077
