<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    BREWER'S DEFENSE IMPRESSES HEAT WITH 51ST PICK
 &HT;    By TOM D'ANGELO
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
