men's basketball Final Four for 2003-05, with Atlanta and the
Georgia Dome expected to win one of the bids. The Final Four is
already slated for Atlanta in 2002. (Schlabach, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) ETA: 8 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   BOWLING-VOSS _ Brian Voss has made a Hall of Fame career out of
a sport typically personified by balding, beer-gutted men in need
of recreation. Voss certainly doesn't fit that description. He's
appeared in a couple of movies and his striking good looks spawned
actress Lauren Bacall's interest in professional bowling. Chances
are, though, few in Atlanta have ever heard of the guy. ``I don't
mind that,'' the 39-year-old Roswell resident said. ``I love what I
do.'' And that's win. (MLee, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) ETA: 8
p.m.
