<P>
   NATIONAL
</P>
<P>
   FIRES _ ORMOND BEACH, Fla. _ Hundreds of residents left their
neighborhood west of Ormond Beach in an orderly procession of old
pickup trucks and sedans filled with pets, clothes and valuables as
a wildfire moved toward their homes. (Staletovich., Palm Beach
Post)
</P>
<P>
   FAGAN _ BOSTON _ William Fagan arraignment today, a lot of
discovery exchanged at hearing. (Holland, Palm Beach Post)
</P>
<P>
   ORANGE _ WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ The latest commercial for
Minute Maid orange juice _ just like eating a ripe Florida orange _
features a beautiful specimen of the fruit. There's just one
problem: it's a California orange. Our local agricultural extension
agent confirms: ``That was my thought exactly. It's a California
orange.'' (Kleinberg, Palm Beach Post)
</P>
<P>
   ECOLI0626 _ Updating number of new cases, how many states
involved, where the investigation is going; health officials were
