<P>
   &UR; INTERNATIONAL (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   CHINA-CLINTON (Xian, China) _ Amid pageantry, controversy and
hope, President Clinton arrives at the gates to China's ancient
capital to begin a nine-day journey. By Brian McGrory. 1100 words.
</P>
<P>
   w/
