   &UR; SPORTS (s) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   BBA-REDSOX-PHILLIES (Philadelphia) _ By Gordon Edes.
</P>
<P>
   SOC-US-YUGO (Nantes, France) _ Yugoslavs take a 1-0 victory, but
they are unable to turn match against the US into a goal-fest in an
effort to overtake Germany for first place in Group F. By Frank
Dell'Apa.
</P>
<P>
   w/
</P>
<P>
   SOC-WORLDCUP-COMMENT (Paris) -- By John Powers.
</P>
<P>
   TEN-COLLINS-COLUMN (London) -- For Andre Agassi and Jennifer
Capriati and Wimbledown, it's thanks for the memories. By Bud
Collins.
</P>
<P>
   HKN-EXPANSION (Buffalo, N.Y.) _ By Friday afternoon the
Nashville Predators will finally have names and faces that will
fill the franchise's shirts for the start of its inaugural National
Hockey League season. By Kevin Paul Dupont. (2 takes)
</P>
