800 words.
</P>
<P>
   MICROSOFT-98 (Undated) -- With little fanfare, Microsoft rolls
out Windows 98 after scoring what may be a significant victory
against the Justice Department's efforts to force the company to
separate its web browser from the new operating system
software. &UR;  &LR; By Hiawatha Bray. 900 words.
</P>
