<DOCNO> NYT19980625.0362 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-25 18:50 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7286 &Cx1f; taf-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ON-LANGUAGE-$ADV28-NY     06-25 1000
