<P>
   (NYT8) NEW YORK -- June 25, 1998 -- MEDIA-BRILL-BOS, 6-25 --
Steven Brill, editor and publisher of Brill's Content, in his
Manhattan office. In starting a magazine of media criticism, Brill,
47, obviously wanted to watch the watchers. The grand irony is that
he is now the most scrutinized man on the media radar screen. ``No
more Mr. Nice Guy,'' he says with a sly smile. (Tom Herde/Boston
Globe Photo) *LITE
