<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-25 23:48 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7904 &Cx1f; ttc-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-VIRAL-MENIN     06-25 0028
</HEADER>
